; Regression test for issue #763: Error: Cannot convert a balance with multiple commodities to an amount (BZ#763)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/763
;
; This issue reported an error "Cannot convert a balance with multiple commodities
; to an amount" when reporting on accounts that hold multiple commodities.
; The basic balance report on a multi-commodity account should work without errors.

2023/01/01 Buy stocks
    Assets:Portfolio   10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

2023/01/02 Buy bonds
    Assets:Portfolio   5 BOND @ $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal Assets:Portfolio
             10 AAPL
              5 BOND  Assets:Portfolio
end test
